{"type":"message","id":"3550d5af","parentId":"a9753195","timestamp":"2026-03-05T08:41:20.346Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我们遇到了一个问题：原本计划运行的脚本 `stocks_monitor.py` 并不存在。根据对技能目录的检查，我们发现 `stock-watcher` 技能的 `scripts` 目录下并没有这个文件，而是有 `summarize_performance.py` 等脚本。\n\n考虑到任务名称是“股票监控”，并且 `summarize_performance.py` 听起来像是用来汇总股票表现的，我决定尝试运行这个脚本。\n\n但是，在运行 `summarize_performance.py` 后，没有产生任何输出，这可能是因为脚本没有设计为输出到标准输出，或者它需要参数。\n\n让我们查看一下 `summarize_performance.py` 的内容，以了解它的功能和使用方法。\n\n使用 `read` 工具读取 `/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/stock-watcher/scripts/summarize_performance.py` 文件的内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"脚本运行没有输出，这可能意味着脚本没有执行任何操作或需要参数。让我检查脚本内容以确定其用途：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f812fa579ced44a0b6a4e9","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/stock-watcher/scripts/summarize_performance.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"deepseek-r1","usage":{"input":15552,"output":452,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16004,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772700071530}}
{"type":"message","id":"e09b5d43","parentId":"3550d5af","timestamp":"2026-03-05T08:41:20.351Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f812fa579ced44a0b6a4e9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nSummarize the performance of all stocks in the watchlist.\nThis script fetches current stock data from 10jqka.com.cn for each stock\nin the watchlist and provides a summary of their recent performance.\n\"\"\"\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport requests\nfrom bs4 import BeautifulSoup\nimport time\n\n# Standardized watchlist file path\nWATCHLIST_FILE = os.path.expanduser(\"~/.clawdbot/stock_watcher/watchlist.txt\")\n\ndef fetch_stock_data(stock_code):\n    \"\"\"Fetch stock data from 10jqka.com.cn.\"\"\"\n    url = f\"https://stockpage.10jqka.com.cn/{stock_code}/\"\n    \n    try:\n        headers = {\n            'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/91.0.4472.124 Safari/537.36'\n        }\n        response = requests.get(url, headers=headers, timeout=10)\n        response.encoding = 'utf-8'\n        \n        if response.status_code != 200:\n            return None\n            \n        soup = BeautifulSoup(response.text, 'html.parser')\n        \n        # Extract basic info\n        title = soup.find('title')\n        stock_name = \"\"\n        if title:\n            title_text = title.get_text()\n            if '(' in title_text and ')' in title_text:\n                stock_name = title_text.split('(')[0].strip()\n        \n        # Look for performance data\n        performance_data = {}\n        \n        # Try to find recent performance indicators\n        # This is a simplified version - in practice, you'd need more robust parsing\n        text_content = soup.get_text()\n        \n        # Look for key phrases\n        if '涨跌幅' in text_content:\n            # Extract percentage changes\n            import re\n            percentages = re.findall(r'[-+]?\\d+\\.?\\d*%', text_content)\n            if percentages:\n                performance_data['recent_changes'] = percentages[:3]  # Get first 3 percentages\n        \n        return {\n            'code': stock_code,\n            'name': stock_name,\n            'url': url,\n            'performance': performance_data\n        }\n        \n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Error fetching data for {stock_code}: {e}\", file=sys.stderr)\n        return None\n\ndef summarize_performance():\n    \"\"\"Summarize performance of all stocks in watchlist.\"\"\"\n    if not os.path.exists(WATCHLIST_FILE):\n        return\n    \n    with open(WATCHLIST_FILE, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        lines = f.readlines()\n    \n    if not lines or all(not line.strip() for line in lines):\n        return\n    \n    # Directly output performance summary without any command prompts\n    for line in lines:\n        line = line.strip()\n        if line:\n            parts = line.split('|')\n            if len(parts) == 2:\n                code, name = parts\n                \n                # Fetch data\n                stock_data = fetch_stock_data(code)\n                if stock_data:\n                    if stock_data['performance']:\n                        for i, change in enumerate(stock_data['performance'].get('recent_changes', []), 1):\n                            print(f\"{code} - {name} - 指标{i}: {change}\")\n                    else:\n                        print(f\"{code} - {name} - 行情数据暂不可用\")\n                else:\n                    print(f\"{code} - {name} - 获取数据失败\")\n                \n                # Be respectful to the server\n                time.sleep(1)\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    summarize_performance()"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772700080349}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae8f6aa1","parentId":"e09b5d43","timestamp":"2026-03-05T08:41:34.811Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我们尝试运行了股票监控脚本，但遇到了文件路径错误。经过检查，发现脚本目录中并没有`stocks_monitor.py`文件，而是有`summarize_performance.py`。因此，我们改为运行这个脚本。\n\n 然而，运行`summarize_performance.py`后没有输出。我们读取了该脚本的内容，发现它的功能是读取股票观察列表中的股票，然后从10jqka.com.cn获取每只股票的近期表现（涨跌幅）并打印。\n\n 没有输出的原因可能是观察列表文件为空或不存在。根据脚本，观察列表文件位于`~/.clawdbot/stock_watcher/watchlist.txt`。\n\n 因此，我们需要检查这个观察列表文件是否存在以及是否有内容。\n\n 步骤：\n 1. 检查观察列表文件是否存在：`ls ~/.clawdbot/stock_watcher/watchlist.txt`\n 2. 如果存在，读取其内容：`read ~/.clawdbot/stock_watcher/watchlist.txt`\n 3. 如果不存在，则说明观察列表为空，因此脚本没有输出。\n\n 由于这是一个定时任务，我们需要将结果反馈给用户。如果观察列表为空，则返回提示信息；如果有内容但脚本没有输出，则可能是网络问题或解析问题。\n\n 但注意：我们之前运行脚本时没有报错，只是没有输出。因此，我们先检查文件是否存在。\n\n 注意：当前工作目录是`/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace`，但脚本中使用了绝对路径`~/.clawdbot/stock_watcher/watchlist.txt`，而`~`在脚本中会被扩展为当前用户的家目录，即`/home/openclaw`。\n\n 我们执行以下命令来检查文件：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看来脚本尝试从`~/.clawdbot/stock_watcher/watchlist.txt`读取股票列表，但该文件可能不存在或为空。让我检查该文件是否存在：\n\n1. 检查股票观察列表文件是否存在\n2. 如果存在，读取其内容\n3. 如果不存在，说明需要先添加股票到观察列表\n\n首先检查文件是否存在：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ef91fc17bf9246beb63f63","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.clawdbot/stock_watcher/watchlist.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"deepseek-r1","usage":{"input":1204,"output":854,"cacheRead":15166,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17224,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772700080351}}
